CUCC Held the Business Conference for Elites from Shandong in New Jersey\n\n

  	On August 9th, 2012, &quot;Shandong Province (eastern United States) Talent Recruitment&quot;, sponsored by Shandong province government and co-organized by China&mdash;U.S. Chamber of Commerce (CUCC), was held in New Jersey. Mr.Hu Wenrong who is the Deputy Minister of the Organization Department of Shandong Province Party Committee and the director of the Leading Group Office of Shandong Province, led the executives from the relevant departments of Shandong province government, Shandong Province Academy of Agricultural Sciences and other research institutes, China Ocean University and other famous universities, parts of state-level economic development zones, high-tech zones, Shandong Heavy Industry Group Company Limited,Hualu Holding Co., Ltd, Inspur Group Company Limited, and other province-level large business companies to gather in New York to participate in this recruitment. More than 220 people from science and technology, economic and trade fields in the great New York area attended the recruitment.

  	&nbsp;

  	Before the recruitment, the delegation visited the Chinese Consulate General in New York and gave an introduction of the exchanges of the high-level overseas talents and this recruitment to Mr. Dong Xiaojun, the Deputy Consul General, and expressed thanks to the strong support from Consulate General. Mr. Dong introduced the characteristics of the high-level overseas talents in great New York area as well as the important role that the high-tech talents played in scientific and technological exchanges. He also stated that the Consulate General would continue to support and assist Shandong Province in various fields and keep the friendship and cooperation.

  	&nbsp;

  	The recruitment was hosted by Mr. Sun Jianbo, the deputy director of Shandong Province Department of Commerce. Mr. Ye Dongbo, the Counselor for Science &amp; Technology of China in New York, participated in the recruitment and delivered a speech. Mr. Ye said that economic development in Shandong Province was in the first in Chinaand Shandong province government had made remarkable achievements in the exchanges of overseas talents. The prosperity and development of China provided the overseas students, professionals and the enterprise enormous opportunities for development. He sincerely hoped that the professionals in great New York area could continue to care for and support the construction and development of China and provide services for China&rsquo;s construction in various ways and realize their own values and ideals.

  	&nbsp;

  	Mr. Hu Wenrong, the director of Shandong Province introduced the achievements gained from the programs: &quot;Thousands of People Plan&quot;, &quot;Young Thousand Talents Program&quot; and &quot;Overseas Experts thousands Plan&rdquo; in recent years, and presented the &ldquo;Taishan Scholar Embodiment&rdquo;. Mr. Zhang Dayong, the west coast of Qingdao Economic Area Administrative Committee Director, Mr. Bao Jianying, the chairman of the Shandong Marine Investment Corporation, and Ms. Guo Qin, the deputy general manager of Hualu Holding Co., Ltd, respectively made a key-note speech in the recruitment.
